translate german rebap2_7c5d53c3:

    # rb "Anything really. I mostly just want the college experience."
    rb "Egal was. Ich will vor allem einfach das College-Leben erleben."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap2.rpy:13
translate german rebap2_7a0705d4:

    # rb "To be around other people from different cultures and lifestyles."
    rb "Mit anderen Menschen aus verschiedenen Kulturen und mit unterschiedlichen Lebensweisen zusammen sein."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap2.rpy:14
translate german rebap2_339bef55:

    # rb "So it really doesn't matter."
    rb "Also ist es eigentlich egal."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap2.rpy:15
translate german rebap2_ec0494f3:

    # pc "But you have to pick a major eventually when you go to college... do you have any idea what it would be?"
    pc "Aber irgendwann musst du dir ja ein Hauptfach aussuchen, wenn du aufs College gehst … hast du schon eine Idee, was das sein könnte?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap2.rpy:16
translate german rebap2_132f7378:

    # rb "I guess engineering, or something like that."
    rb "Ich schätze Ingenieurwesen oder so was in der Art."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap2.rpy:17
translate german rebap2_5983338d:

    # rb "I like to build stuff. I like to see how things work."
    rb "Ich baue gerne Sachen. Ich mag es zu sehen, wie Dinge funktionieren."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap2.rpy:19
translate german rebap2_a653762f:

    # rb "I think I'd be good at that."
    rb "Ich glaube, darin wäre ich gut."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap2.rpy:20
translate german rebap2_2e0b8e20:

    # pc "I know you would."
    pc "Das glaube ich dir."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap2.rpy:21
translate german rebap2_60889a8b:

    # pc "I hope I get to see you do it."
    pc "Ich hoffe, ich darf dir dabei zusehen."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebap2.rpy:22
translate german rebap2_7cbe57ac:

    # rb "Thanks, [pcname]. Me too."
    rb "Danke, [pcname]. Ich auch."

